rwitz-composing-music-lifelong-obsession/98029448/|title=Oscar-nominated 'La La Land' composer Justin Hurwitz got his start in Milwaukee|author=|last=Levy|first=Piet|date=February 17, 2017|work=|newspaper=Milwaukee Journal Sentinel|accessdate=June 5, 2018|language=}}</ref>。他中学就读于[[威斯康辛州|威斯康辛州]]Glendale的Nicolet High School<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jsonline.com/story/entertainment/movies/2017/01/08/nicolets-justin-hurwitz-wins-2-golden-globes/96325914/|title=Nicolet's Justin Hurwitz wins 2 Golden Globes|date=January 9, 2017|author=Chris Foran|work=[[Milwaukee_Journal_Sentinel|Milwaukee Journal Sentinel]]}}</ref>。在[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]就读时与达米恩·查泽雷是室友和同一乐队成员<ref name="wheretowatch" />。

